quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,So does he not know when what (is) in the graves/burial places is scattered/over thrown/strewn
  100,10,And what (is) in the chests (innermosts) is recovered/collected
  100,11,That truly their Lord (is) with them (on) that day expert/experienced (E)
  101,1,The resurrection/disaster/calamity
  101,2,What (is) the resurrection/disaster/calamity
  101,3,And what made you know/informed you what the resurrection/disaster/calamity (is)
  101,4,"A day/time the people be/become like the butterflies, the scattered/ravished"
  101,5,"And the mountains be/become like the wool/dyed wool, the carded (ruffled)"
  101,6,So as for who his weights became heavy
  101,7,So he is in (an) acceptable/approved life/quality of life
  101,8,And but who his weights were reduced/lightened
  101,9,So his origin (is) Hell/destruction
  101,10,And what made you know/informed you what it is (E)
  101,11,hot fire
  102,1,The multiplication distracted/diverted you
  102,2,Until you visited the cemeteries/burial places
  102,3,No but you will/shall know
  102,4,Then no but you will/shall know
  102,5,No but if you know knowledge (of) the assurance/certainty
  102,6,You would see/understand (E) the Hell
  102,7,Then you will see/understand it (with) the assurance`s/certainty`s eye (visually)
  102,8,Then (on) that day you will be asked/questioned (E) about the blessing/goodness
  103,1,And/by the time/era/end of day to dusk
  103,2,That truly the human/mankind (is) in (E) loss
  103,3,"Except those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, and directed/commanded with the truth/just , and directed/commanded with the patience"
  104,1,"Calamity/scandal/woe to every/each backbiter/spurrer , defamer/blamer"
  104,2,Who gathered/accumulated property/possession/wealth and he counted it repeatedly
  104,3,He thinks/supposes that (E) his property/possession/wealth made him immortal/eternal
  104,4,No but he will be discarded/thrown away (E) in the intense fire/Hell
  104,5,And what made you know/informed you what the intense fire/Hell (is)
  104,6,"God`s fire, the ignited/kindled"
  104,7,Which ascends/rises on (to) the hearts
  104,8,That it truly is on them stationary/residing
  104,9,In extended/spread pillars/posts
  105,1,Did you not see/understand how (what) your Lord made/did with the elephant`s owners/company/ friends
  105,2,Did He not make their plotting/conspiring in misguidance
  105,3,And He sent on them flying/birds (in) flocks/groups gathered and following each other
  105,4,It throws them with stones from dry and hardened mud
  105,5,So He made them like eaten husk/chaff/leaves
  106,1,To Koreish`s unification/familiarity
  106,2,Their unification/familiarization (with) the winter`s and the summer`s travel/journey
  106,3,"So they should worship this, the House`s/Home`s Lord"
  106,4,"Who fed them from starvation/hunger, and secured them from fear/fright"
  107,1,Did you see/understand who lies/denies/falsifies with the religion
  107,2,So that (is) who turns down/repels the orphan
  107,3,And does not urge/insight/influence on feeding the poorest of poor/poor oppressed
  107,4,So calamity/scandal/woe to the prayers (praying people)
  107,5,Those whom they are about their prayers negligent/inattentive
  107,6,Those whom they are pretending/showing off (what they are not)
  107,7,And they prevent/stop the charity
  108,1,"We (E), We gave/granted you the abundance (of goodness)"
  108,2,"So pray to your Lord, and be perfect/excellent/slaughter (for charity)"
  108,3,"That truly your hater and enemy, he is the mean and despised/of no good"
  109,1,"Say: \"You, you the disbelievers"
  109,2,I do not worship what you worship
  109,3,And you are not worshipping what I worship
  109,4,And nor I am worshipping what you worshipped
  109,5,And nor you are worshipping what I worship
  109,6,"For you (is) your religion, and for me (is) my religion"
  110,1,"When/if God`s victory/aid came, and the opening/judgment"
  110,2,And you saw the people entering in God`s religion (in) groups/crowds
  110,3,"So praise/glorify with your Lord`s praise/gratitude/thanks, and ask him for forgiveness, that He truly was/is forgiving"
  111,1,"Father of the flame of a smokeless fire`s (known as Prophet Mohammad`s uncle) hand was destroyed/lost, and destroyed/lost"
  111,2,His property/possession/wealth and what he gained/acquired did not enrich/suffice from him
  111,3,He will roast/suffer/burn (in) a fire that of (a) flame of smokeless fire
  111,4,And his woman (wife) the fire wood`s/fuel`s carrier/lifter
  111,5,In her neck/beautiful neck (is a) rope from palm fiber tightly woven rope/an iron ring
  112,1,"Say: \"He is God one"
  112,2,God the Lord/master/intended
  112,3,"(He) did not give birth/procreate , and was not born/procreated"
  112,4,And (there) was not for Him any equal/match
  113,1,"Say: \"I seek protection with/by Lord/master/owner (of) the daybreak/creation"
  113,2,From bad/evil/harm (of) what He created
  113,3,"And from bad/evil/harm (of an) intense dark night/moon, when/if (it) penetrated through body pores/ spread/approached"
  113,4,And from bad/evil/harm (of) the female magicians/sorceresses/dischargers in the knots
  113,5,"And from bad/evil/harm (of) an envious with jealousy , when/if he envied with jealousy"
  114,1,"Say: \"I seek protection with/by the people`s Lord/master/owner"
  114,2,The people`s king/owner/possessor
  114,3,The people`s God
  114,4,"From bad/evil/harm (of) the inspirer and talker/giver of evil suggestions and temptations (whisperer of evil influences), the devil"
  114,5,Who inspires and talks/gives evil suggestions and temptations in the people`s chests (innermosts)
  114,6,From the Jinns and the people